# === Test / verification screenshots (anywhere in the repo) ===
# Catches screenshots taken by Unity's manage_camera, chrome-devtools-mcp's
# take_screenshot, or any ad-hoc verification shots. Use /tmp for transient
# captures, or commit purposefully under Assets/Art/ as procedural source.
[Ss]creenshots/
*-screenshot.png
*-screenshot.jpg
*-screenshot.webp
verification-*.png
smoke-*.png

# === Local tooling (not the project) ===
.claude/
.remember/

# === User's private scratch notes (not for Claude to read unless directed) ===
todo.md

# === Identity scrub patterns (see tools/identity-scrub.py) ===
# Gitignored so the identity tokens themselves never land in the repo.
# Populate on fresh clones from CLAUDE.md / feedback_identity_leaks.md.
.claude-identity-scrub
